query: SELECT p.id, c.name as country, s.name as service, p.smshubPrice, p.ourPrice FROM prices p JOIN countries c ON p.countryId = c.id JOIN services s ON p.serviceId = s.id ORDER BY p.smshubPrice DESC LIMIT 10
